ygData.messageBody:
Hello,

There is a new survey for the warriors_eq community.

What is your warrior's deity, the Warlord, Rallos Zek, or someone else?

----

o SOLUSEK RO - THE BURNING PRINCE
o MITHANIEL MARR - THE LIGHTBEARER
o TUNARE - THE MOTHER OF ALL
o VEESHAN - THE WURMQUEEN
o BRISTLEBANE - THE KING OF THIEVES
o CAZIC-THULE - THE FACELESS
o INNORUUK - THE PRINCE OF HATE
o KARANA - THE RAINKEEPER
o EROLLISI MARR - THE QUEEN OF LOVE
o RODCET NIFE - THE PRIME HEALER
o PREXUS - THE OCEANLORD
o QUELLIOUS - THE TRANQUIL
o BRELL SERILIS - THE DUKE OF BELOW
o TAREW MARR


To vote, please visit the following web page:

http://www.onelist.com/surveycenter/warriors_eq


Thanks!
